annotations.title: Do You Frappe Your Daiquiri? You Should!

textContent:
2oz (60ml) White Rum
.75oz (22.5ml) Lime Juice
2.5 Tbsp Cane Sugar
1.5 Cups Pebble Ice
1 Tsp Lime Zest
Lime Zest Garnish

Blend in blender and pour into large coupe
